bsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:24.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院主院区负二层病案库病案架采购及安装项目 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:24.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路<span>66</span>号）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院主院区负二层病案库病案架采购及安装项目，具体货物名称、数量、规格及技术参数等以招标文件、技术要求、采购清单为准，招标人保留对上述招标范围进行适当调整的权利。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">质量标准：符合国家“合格”标准，质保期<span>2</span>年。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.5 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">供货期要求：<u><span>15</span></u>日历天，具体开工日期以招标人的通知。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">最高限价：<u><span>17.55 </span></u>万元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:24.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2 </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">投标人应当具备的主要资格条件：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">投标人必须是在中国境内注册，有独立完成本项目所有工作的能力的独立法人。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目负责人为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止之日当月向前连续<span>6</span>个月均已在本单位缴纳养老保险（例：如开标日期为<span>2023</span>年<span>2</span>月的某一天，则投标人需保证以上人员<span>2022</span>年<span>7</span>月<span>-2023</span>年<span>1</span>月养老保险均在本单位缴纳）（投标时提供社保证明材料）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">其他要求<span><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.3.1</span>财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。<span>&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.3.2</span>信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.4 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;background:white\"><span style=\"background:white\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">8</span><span style=\"background:white\">号</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">8</span><span style=\"background:white\">楼</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">805</span><span style=\"background:white\">室）投标报名并领取招标文件，投标报名时间</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">2023</span><span style=\"background:\r\nwhite\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">4</span><span style=\"background:white\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">\r\n<span>7</span></span><span style=\"background:white\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">8</span><span style=\"background:white\">时</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">30</span><span style=\"background:white\">分至</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">2023</span><span style=\"background:white\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">4</span><span style=\"background:white\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">13</span><span style=\"background:white\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">18</span><span style=\"background:white\">时。联系人：刘工，</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">0515-69057406</span><span style=\"background:white\">；手机：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">13626222271</span><span style=\"background:white\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;background:white\"><span style=\"font-f